These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, black, green, turquise
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, country, r&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, hot-chocolate, fanta
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, chess, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, subway, tram
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person who likes green is not the person driving the car##6
 4. the person driving the subway is not the person who likes black##6
 5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 7. the person driving the tram is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
 8. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of blues##1
 9. the fan of country is not the person who likes turquise##6
10. the fan of r&b is the person driving the car##1
11. the fan of country is the person driving the boat##1
12. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
14. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
15. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
16. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the tram##7
17. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person drinking mirinda##6
18. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
19. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the fan of blues and the person who's sport is baseball##7
20. the person playing canasta is not the person who likes turquise##6
21. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Color          | coral      | turquise   | black     | green |
| Music-Genre           | r&b | gospel   | blues    | country     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | time-travel | horror   | mystery   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | fanta     | mirinda | cola    |
| Game           | canasta   | mah-jongg       | chess  | snooker       |
| Sport         | baseball     | cycling     | handball | parkour   |
| Transport     | car          | subway      | tram     | boat      |

